<h3>Sign up!</h3>

<p>
  You need to have an account with us to contribute.  Please sign up below.  
  After you submit this form, we'll send you a note to confirm your email address, 
  and then you can log in.
</p>
<p>
  <b>Submission guidelines:</b>  You may submit up to five poems or one work of short prose (c. 3500 words). Simultaneous submissions are acceptable, provided that you let us know if you're accepted elsewhere. We enjoy a wide range of styles and genresâ€”what we want most are pieces that demonstrate a clear voice, unafraid to be passionate and reveling in sound.
</p>

<% form_for :user, @user || User.new, :url => users_path do |f| -%>

<div>
  <%= f.label :email %>
  <br/>
  <%= f.text_field :email, :class => "text" %>
  <%= f.error_message_on :email %>
</div>

<div>
  <%= f.label :password %>
  <br/>
  <%= f.password_field :password, :class => "text" %>
  <%= f.error_message_on :password %>
</div>

<div>
  <%= f.label :password_confirmation, "Confirm Password" %>
  <br/>
  <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, :class => "text" %>
  <%= f.error_message_on :password_confirmation %>
</div>

<p><%= submit_tag 'Sign up', :class => "button" %></p>
<% end -%>
